---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "GE Café Dishwasher Repair Los Angeles — Same Day";
const description = "GE Café dishwasher repair across SoCal, CDT series, brass / matte black / matte white customizable handles, panel-ready. $89 dx.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/ge-cafe-dishwasher-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Where does GE Café sit in the GE Appliances dishwasher lineup?",
    a: "GE Café is GE Appliances' style-first premium tier, positioned alongside GE Profile at premium pricing ($1,400-$2,200 retail) but differentiated by style-forward design language instead of Profile's feature-density pitch. Café's signature is customizable exterior hardware: brushed brass, matte black, matte white, and stainless-steel handle + knob options that coordinate with Café refrigeration, ranges, cooktops, and wall ovens. Café dishwashers deliver premium engineering spec (42 dB typical, stainless-tub baseline, Dry Boost, Bottle Jets, SmartHQ) while trading some of Profile's feature-density for Café's visible-design premium appeal. For LA kitchen remodels where the Café look coordinates across the appliance suite, the dishwasher is the expected spec. Relative positioning: below GE Monogram (ultra-luxury panel-ready), alongside GE Profile (feature-premium), above mainstream GE."
  },
  {
    q: "What GE Café dishwasher models are most common in LA?",
    a: "CDT series dominates LA GE Café dishwasher installs. CDT805, CDT835, CDT855, CDT875 families are 24-inch built-in with Café design language, brushed-brass / matte-black / matte-white / stainless-steel customizable hardware, stainless-steel tub + interior, 42 dB noise profile, Dry Boost fan-assist drying, Bottle Jets tall-item zone, SmartHQ Wi-Fi with premium app integration. Most Café dishwashers ship with customizable handle + knob kits (sold separately or bundled) so the installed unit matches the kitchen's Café appliance suite. LA Café dishwasher service concentrates in design-forward premium kitchens: Westside premium remodels (Brentwood, Pacific Palisades, Mar Vista), Hollywood Hills custom kitchens, Encino + Calabasas Valley premium, design-conscious Silver Lake / Los Feliz / Highland Park eastside (Café is a common alternative spec to Smeg FAB in these design-conscious neighborhoods), Pasadena + San Marino, Orange County premium."
  },
  {
    q: "Our Café dishwasher's brass handle is tarnishing / the matte finish is scratching, is that a service item?",
    a: "Yes, handle + knob replacement is a real Café service item. Café's brushed brass, matte black, matte white, and stainless finishes are durable but show wear over years on daily-use households. Tarnish on brass (particularly in kitchens with heavy humidity or coastal air), scratching on matte finishes (door-handle grip area especially), chip damage on knob hardware, all are visible-surface wear that degrades Café's design-forward appeal. Service: handle + knob replacement kits sold individually, quoted $140–$280 typical depending on finish (matte finishes sometimes slightly higher than brushed stainless due to finish-spec production). We coordinate with GE Appliances Café parts channel for color-matched hardware; typical 3-7 day lead on standard finishes, 7-14 day on brushed brass on occasion when brass hardware has higher-than-usual demand. Interior hardware (rack slides, tine adjustment) service is standard GE Profile-equivalent pricing."
  },
  {
    q: "Our Café dishwasher has SmartHQ issues, is that different from Profile SmartHQ?",
    a: "Same SmartHQ platform, same integration architecture, same service approach. SmartHQ is GE Appliances' unified smart-home platform across all four tiers (mainstream GE, Profile, Café, Monogram). Café's SmartHQ integration is functionally identical to Profile's, Wi-Fi module (2.4GHz only on older generations, dual-band on newer), fault-code display in app, remote-start where supported, cycle-status notifications, recipe-integration features. Common disconnection causes match the broader SmartHQ pattern: router-side reconfig needs, 2.4GHz vs 5GHz password confusion, ThinQ / SmartThings cross-app conflicts, ThinQ account changes. Service approach: $89 diagnostic visit resolves 95% of SmartHQ disconnection calls via network-side reconfig; actual Wi-Fi module failure rare and $180–$280 swap when hardware diagnostic confirms. Café owners sometimes report 'Café appliance suite lost connectivity', usually a single-router issue affecting all Café appliances simultaneously, not per-appliance hardware failure."
  },
  {
    q: "What does GE Café dishwasher repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic is $89, waived when you authorize the repair. Common Café bands: drain filter clean $89 (often free at diagnostic); drain pump $240–$380; inlet valve $260–$400; door latch + switch $220–$340; door gasket $240–$400; heating element $280–$440; Dry Boost service $260–$420; Bottle Jets + silverware jet $140–$240; Piranha disposer service same as mainstream GE $180–$340; customizable handle + knob hardware replacement $140–$280 per item depending on finish; SmartHQ Wi-Fi module (reconfig usually resolves) $180–$280; control board (premium Café electronics) $420–$640; membrane switch + premium panel $280–$460; circulation pump $440–$640. Café hardware parts through GE Appliances Café channel; typical 3-7 day on common items, 7-14 day on brushed-brass and specialty finishes. Café service runs similar economics to Profile on mechanical items, Café-specific on handle + design hardware."
  },

    {
      q: "Where can I find the official GE manual or warranty information?",
      a: `For official GE documentation, warranty registration, and authorized service locator, visit <a href="https://www.geappliances.com/service/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">GE Appliances service</a>. Our technicians work independently of GE's factory service network - we're often faster and available same-day in Southern California.`
    },
  ];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair, GE Café Dishwasher Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL, "priceRange": "$$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "GE Café Dishwasher Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "GE Café dishwasher repair across Southern California, LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. CDT series, customizable brushed brass / matte black / matte white / stainless handles, 42 dB noise, Dry Boost, Bottle Jets, SmartHQ. Style-first premium GE tier. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "GE Café", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/ge-cafe/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "GE Café Dishwasher Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>GE Café dishwasher service? Same-day across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › GE Café › Dishwasher Repair</div>
    <h1>GE Café Dishwasher Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">GE Café is GE Appliances' style-first premium tier, CDT series 24-inch built-in dishwashers with customizable brushed brass, matte black, matte white, and stainless-steel handle + knob hardware that coordinates across the Café refrigeration / range / cooktop / wall oven appliance suite. Premium engineering spec (42 dB, Dry Boost, Bottle Jets, SmartHQ Wi-Fi) combined with visible-design premium appeal distinguishes Café from Profile's feature-density positioning. Our LA Café dishwasher service concentrates in design-forward premium kitchens across Westside, Hollywood Hills, Encino + Calabasas, Silver Lake + Los Feliz (design-conscious eastside), Pasadena + San Marino, and Orange County premium. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
    <ul class="hero-facts">
      <li><b>GE Appliances style-first premium tier</b>, Haier-owned since 2016</li>
      <li><b>Customizable handles</b>, brushed brass / matte black / matte white / stainless</li>
      <li><b>CDT series</b>, 24" built-in with 42 dB + Dry Boost + Bottle Jets + SmartHQ</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b>, waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>BHGS #A49573 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>GE Café across Southern California, style-first premium, design-forward kitchens</h2>
    <p>GE Café's design-premium positioning differs from GE Profile's feature-density pitch. Where Profile emphasizes UltraFresh + Microban + SmartHQ stack depth, Café emphasizes visible design, customizable brushed brass / matte black / matte white / stainless handle + knob hardware that coordinates across a Café-branded kitchen suite. For remodels where the kitchen's aesthetic identity is the spec-driver, Silver Lake design-conscious loft, Highland Park mid-century renovation, Brentwood custom remodel, Hollywood Hills architectural kitchen on the LA side; Newport Beach contemporary builds, Costa Mesa designer kitchens in OC; Westlake Village and Calabasas modern estates in Ventura; and Rancho Cucamonga and Temecula wine-country contemporary homes in the IE, Café delivers the coordinated-design premium look at mid-premium pricing ($1,400-$2,200 retail dishwasher, $2,500-$5,000+ Café refrigerator).</p>
    <p>Café dishwasher service geography across our service area concentrates in distinct design-demographic zones. Design-conscious eastside: Silver Lake, Los Feliz, Highland Park, Mount Washington, Echo Park, where Café is a common spec alternative to Smeg FAB in design-forward mid-century renovations. Premium westside + canyon: Brentwood, Pacific Palisades, Hollywood Hills, Mar Vista, custom remodels with coordinated Café appliance suite. Plus Encino / Calabasas Valley premium and Pasadena + San Marino on the LA side; Orange County premium (Newport Beach, Irvine, Laguna Beach, Costa Mesa); Conejo Valley contemporary (Thousand Oaks, Westlake Village); and IE contemporary estates (Rancho Cucamonga, Temecula wine-country).</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>GE Café dishwasher failures our techs see most often</h2>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Customizable handle + knob hardware wear</h3><p>Brushed brass tarnish, matte finish scratch, knob chip damage at 5-8 years daily-use. Hardware replacement $140–$280 per item depending on finish.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Drain system, standard GE architecture</h3><p>Same drain path as mainstream GE + Profile. Filter often free; drain pump $240–$380; Piranha disposer $180–$340.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Heating element + Dry Boost</h3><p>Element swap $280–$440. Same Dry Boost feature as Profile.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Door gasket</h3><p>6-8 year service $240–$400.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>SmartHQ reconfiguration (same platform as Profile)</h3><p>Router-side fix typical $89 diagnostic visit.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Premium control board + interface</h3><p>Café control electronics $420–$640 board; panel $280–$460.</p></div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>GE Café dishwasher product lines we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>CDT series (volume)</h3><p>CDT805, CDT835, CDT855, CDT875 families. 24-inch built-in with Café design language.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Customizable handle hardware</h3><p>Brushed brass / matte black / matte white / stainless kits. Coordination with Café appliance suite.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>42 dB noise + Dry Boost</h3><p>Premium noise spec + fan-assist drying.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Bottle Jets + Piranha disposer</h3><p>Same tall-items + food-grinder architecture as GE Profile + mainstream GE.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>SmartHQ premium Wi-Fi</h3><p>GE Appliances unified smart-home platform.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Café-coordinated kitchen suite</h3><p>Dishwasher spec matches Café refrigeration / range / cooktop / wall oven hardware.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>GE tier navigation, which combo page fits your dishwasher</h2>
    <p><b>GE (mainstream)</b>, GDT / GDF. See <a href="/brands/ge-dishwasher-repair/">GE dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
    <p><b>GE Profile (feature-focused premium)</b>, PDT / PDP. See <a href="/brands/ge-profile-dishwasher-repair/">GE Profile dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
    <p><b>GE Café (style-first premium)</b>, this page. CDT with customizable handles.</p>
    <p><b>GE Monogram (ultra-luxury)</b>, ZDT / ZBD Statement + Minimalist panel-ready. See <a href="/brands/ge-monogram-dishwasher-repair/">GE Monogram dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
